                            <comment id="12926586" author="sebb@apache.org" created="Sat, 30 Oct 2010 14:50:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;A similar problem happens with prunsrv:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;prunsrv //1234&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;EventType : BEX     P1 : prunsrv.exe     P2 : 1.0.4.0     P3 : 4cbfeb12     &lt;br/&gt;
P4 : prunsrv.exe     P5 : 1.0.4.0     P6 : 4cbfeb12     P7 : 000013d8     &lt;br/&gt;
P8 : c0000409     P9 : 00000000     &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;However&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;&lt;p&gt;prunsrv //123&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;results in:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;2010-10-30 15:48:49&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;error&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Unrecognized cmd option //123&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;2010-10-30 15:48:49&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;error&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Invalid command line arguments&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;2010-10-30 15:48:49&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;error&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt; Commons Daemon procrun failed with exit value: 1 (Failed to parse command line arguments)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;which is better than the prunmgr message.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13044853" author="mturk@apache.org" created="Mon, 6 Jun 2011 14:06:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed in the SVN. Will be part of 1.0.6 release&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
