                            <comment id="12845423" author="mturk@apache.org" created="Mon, 15 Mar 2010 17:48:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;You choose the correct place.&lt;br/&gt;
And this is really a bug. It shouldn&apos;t behave like it does nowadays.&lt;br/&gt;
Will fix that with coming 1.0.3&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12845714" author="mturk@apache.org" created="Tue, 16 Mar 2010 05:16:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Fixed with the 1.0.3&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Using stderr instead displaying MessageBox.&lt;br/&gt;
//US//ServiceName now calls //IS//ServiceName if ServiceName was not installed.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12845772" author="davidnewcomb" created="Tue, 16 Mar 2010 09:25:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks a lot. Don&apos;t forget to update the online documentation.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
