                                    <reporter username="trev">Trev</reporter>
                        <labels>
                    </labels>
                <created>Fri, 6 Feb 2009 00:33:24 +0000</created>
                <updated>Thu, 11 Feb 2010 17:39:48 +0000</updated>
                            <resolved>Thu, 11 Feb 2010 17:39:48 +0000</resolved>
                                    <version>1.0.1</version>
                                                        <due></due>
                            <votes>1</votes>
                                    <watches>3</watches>
                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12832595" author="mturk@apache.org" created="Thu, 11 Feb 2010 17:39:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;JIRA is not support forum.&lt;br/&gt;
You would need a shutdown system similar to tomcat&apos;s &apos;catalina stop&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
which will by using some form of RPC cleanly shutdown your application.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
