                <created>Mon, 31 Mar 2008 10:06:46 +0000</created>
                <updated>Thu, 11 Feb 2010 17:35:47 +0000</updated>
                            <resolved>Thu, 11 Feb 2010 17:35:47 +0000</resolved>
                                                                        <due></due>
                            <votes>0</votes>
                                    <watches>0</watches>
                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12650130" author="caijunj" created="Mon, 24 Nov 2008 07:47:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Try something like this: &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;tomcat6 //TS// ++JvmOptions -Xdebug;-Xrunjdwp:transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=n,address=1044&lt;br/&gt;
or &lt;br/&gt;
tomcat6 //RS// ++JvmOptions -Xdebug;-Xrunjdwp:transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=n,address=1044&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Seems that procrun need the &quot;//command//&quot; if there are other options.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12832592" author="mturk@apache.org" created="Thu, 11 Feb 2010 17:35:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;JIRA is not support forum&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
