exit_group(1)                           = ?&lt;br/&gt;
Process 29655 detached&lt;/p&gt;
</comment>
                            <comment id="12472114" author="betelgeuse" created="Sun, 11 Feb 2007 17:04:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;trunk already seems to be using /proc/self/exe so this can be closed or wait until the fix is in a release version&lt;br/&gt;
       /* execve needs a full path */&lt;br/&gt;
