<item>
            <title>[DAEMON-44] jsvc does not compile due to missing headers</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DAEMON-44</link>
                <project id="12310468" key="DAEMON">Commons Daemon</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The configure miss to add something like&lt;br/&gt;
-I/System/Library/Frameworks/JavaVM.framework/Headers to the CFLAGS when&lt;br/&gt;
compiling java.c. The easy work-around is to add it in Makedefs before compiling.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Operating System: All&lt;br/&gt;
Platform: Macintosh&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
