            <title>[DAEMON-25] Procrun source files contain spurious ^M</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DAEMON-25</link>
                <project id="12310468" key="DAEMON">Commons Daemon</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;After checking out commons-daemon, the procrun files all contain an extra &amp;lt;CR&amp;gt; &lt;br/&gt;
character on every line.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>&lt;p&gt;Operating System: Windows XP&lt;br/&gt;
Platform: PC&lt;/p&gt;</environment>
        <key id="12340990">DAEMON-25</key>
            <summary>Procrun source files contain spurious ^M</summary>
