                <updated>Tue, 14 Nov 2017 15:05:52 +0000</updated>
                            <resolved>Tue, 14 Nov 2017 15:05:52 +0000</resolved>
                                    <version>1.0</version>
                                    <fixVersion>1.0.2</fixVersion>
                                        <due></due>
                            <votes>1</votes>
                                    <watches>0</watches>
                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12407032" author="jfclere@gmail.com" created="Tue, 17 Aug 2004 22:09:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I think I have a similar problem when using a jsp page and JVM 1.4.x:&lt;br/&gt;
+++&lt;br/&gt;
2004-08-17 17:00:24 StandardWrapperValve&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;jsp&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;: Servlet.service() for servlet jsp&lt;br/&gt;
threw exception&lt;br/&gt;
org.apache.jasper.JasperException: Unable to compile class for JSP&lt;br/&gt;
        at&lt;br/&gt;
org.apache.jasper.JspCompilationContext.compile(JspCompilationContext.java:478)&lt;br/&gt;
        at&lt;br/&gt;
org.apache.jasper.servlet.JspServletWrapper.service(JspServletWrapper.java:190)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.jasper.servlet.JspServlet.serviceJspFile(JspServlet.java:295)&lt;br/&gt;
+++&lt;br/&gt;
Root cause:&lt;br/&gt;
+++&lt;br/&gt;
----- Root Cause -----&lt;br/&gt;
java.io.FileNotFoundException:&lt;br/&gt;
/opt/SMAWoIS/jakarta-tomcat/work/Standalone/localhost/examples/jsp/num/numguess_jsp.java&lt;br/&gt;
        at java.io.FileOutputStream.open(Native Method)&lt;br/&gt;
        at java.io.FileOutputStream.&amp;lt;init&amp;gt;(FileOutputStream.java:179)&lt;br/&gt;
        at java.io.FileOutputStream.&amp;lt;init&amp;gt;(FileOutputStream.java:70)&lt;br/&gt;
        at org.apache.jasper.compiler.Compiler.generateJava(Compiler.java:216)&lt;br/&gt;
