But I think I&apos;ve fixed this problem, by compiling CVS version of jsvc.&lt;br/&gt;
I&apos;ve 3.5 weeks uptime with no crash yet, but on standart jsvc I had 1 crash per&lt;br/&gt;
week.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
