(start Tomcat using the shortcut, double click on the tray icon). Please be more&lt;br/&gt;
specific (BTW, tomcatw.exe is the commons-daemon project, so this is not a&lt;br/&gt;
Tomcat bug).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12405140" author="william.barker@wilshire.com" created="Mon, 22 Sep 2003 04:05:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Yes, there is definitely a bug here.  Unless you have your logging levels set &lt;br/&gt;
very high (or are using a particular log4j format) you should see it by simply &lt;br/&gt;
selecting &quot;Open Console&quot; from the menu.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll attach a patch once this is reopened.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
