                            <comment id="12405143" author="william.barker@wilshire.com" created="Mon, 22 Sep 2003 04:09:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Since I don&apos;t have a compiler here, I haven&apos;t tested this.  However it looks &lt;br/&gt;
