<item>
            <title>[DAEMON-1] tomcat.exe --WorkingPath does not set current directory</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DAEMON-1</link>
                <project id="12310468" key="DAEMON">Commons Daemon</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When using tomcat.exe to install tomcat as a service (on Window XP, if it &lt;br/&gt;
matters), the --WorkingPath option appears to have no effect.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I used to do this in tomcat 4, using the (different) version of tomcat.exe &lt;br/&gt;
