karta-tomcat-5.0.18/tmp --ImagePath c:/install/3rdparty/jakarta-tomcat-5.0.18&lt;br/&gt;
/bin/bootstrap.jar --StartupClass &lt;br/&gt;
org.apache.catalina.startup.Bootstrap;main;sta&lt;br/&gt;
rt --ShutdownClass org.apache.catalina.startup.Bootstrap;main;stop &amp;#8211;&lt;br/&gt;
StdOutputFi&lt;br/&gt;
le c:\install\logs\stdout.log --StdErrorFile c:\install\logs\stderr.log &amp;#8211;&lt;br/&gt;
WorkingPath c:/install&lt;/p&gt;</description>
